RES osdtriplet
! ---- CLI: check-clear-apertures computes Y-FAN / X-FAN semi-aperture table ----
CLI
! ---- SPGR: specific gravity query (ALL surfaces, then surface 2) ----
SPGR ALL
SPGR 2
! ---- THM: mirror blank thickness (all-refractive osdtriplet → no data) ----
THM ALL
! ---- COLORSET: set plot color (silent) then query it back ----
COLORSET RAYS 12
COLORSET RAYS ?
! ---- DET: detector settings query ----
DET ?
! ---- CY / CX: ray direction cosines stored to register (print * suppressed) ----
CY f1 w1 s6 0.0 0.7
CX f1 w1 s6 0.0 0.7
! ---- FINDGLAS: help text (query form) then error for non-model glass ----
FINDGLAS ?
FINDGLAS 2 3
! ---- TAR: target loop — add constraint and exit with GO ----
TAR
EFL = 50
GO
LCON
DCON ALL
! ---- UPD CON: update an existing constraint (created with TAR above) ----
TAR
EFL = 50
GO
UPD CON
CHA 1
EFL = 60
GO
LCON
DCON ALL
! ---- Multi-space robustness (parseCommandIntoTokens retirement regression) ----
! Aligned/multi-space commands must parse identically to single-spaced ones;
! the retired tokenizer emitted empty tokens for repeated spaces, silently
! breaking any handler with an exact numTokens check (e.g. aligned STO).
RES osdtriplet
ASP  S2
K  S2  -0.5
SUR SA
SPH  S2
SUR SA

! ---- GLC: glass variable code (bookkeeping only; optimizer support TBD) ----
! GLC Sk 0 marks the glass variable (SUR SA GLC column shows 0);
! GLC Sk 100 freezes it again.
RES osdtriplet
GLC S2 0
SUR SA
GLC S2 100
SUR SA

! ---- TOW: enter loop (FIR is not a zoaCmd so executes; GO not called → no GUI crash) ----
TOW
FIR
